1. *Pametna* devojčica je uspešno završila školu (The intelligent girl successfully finished school).
2. Ona je bila *pametna* dovoljno da shvati situaciju (She was smart enough to understand the situation).
3. On je bio *pametniji* od nje (He was smarter than her).
4. *Pametnije* je da se obratite stručnjaku za pomoć (It's wiser to turn to an expert for help).
5. Oni su se ponašali *pametno* (They acted wisely).